The paper deals with the uplink of a multi-cell Massive MIMO system, which is a topic related to information theory (cs.IT) and networking and internet architecture (cs.NI). The use of spatially correlated Rician fading channels is a topic related to signal processing (cs.SI) and multimedia (cs.MM). Finally, the paper also discusses the performance of channel estimation and combining techniques, which is a topic related to communication (cs.COM).
